593-1996高压开关设备的共用订货技术条件</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">20、IEC420：1990高压交流负荷开关——熔断器组合电器</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">三、设备技术参数：</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">1）XGN2-12型高压开关柜基本技术参数</p><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"671\"><tbody style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><tr style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; height: 19.5pt;\" class=\"firstRow\"><td width=\"344\" style=\"padding: 0cm 5.4pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 19px; border-width: 1pt; border-style: outset; border-color: black; background-color: transparent;\" height=\"19\"><p><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 12pt;\">项　　目</span></p></td><td width=\"48\" style=\"padding: 0cm 5.4pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 19px; border-bottom: 1pt outset black; border-left: rgb(212, 208, 200); background-color: transparent; border-top: 1pt outset black; border-right: 1pt outset black;\" height=\"19\"><p><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 12pt;\">单位</span></p></td><td width=\"232\" style=\"padding: 0cm 5.4pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 19px; border-bottom: 1pt outset black; border-left: rgb(212, 208, 200); background-color: transparent; border-top: 1pt outset black; border-right: 1pt outset black;\" height=\"19\"><p><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 12pt;\">数　　据</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"671\"><tbody style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><tr style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; height: 19.5pt;\" class=\"firstRow\"><td width=\"344\" style=\"padding: 0cm 5.4pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 19px; border-width: 1pt; border-style: outset; border-color: black; background-color: transparent;\" height=\"19\"><p><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 12pt;\">额定电压</span></p></td><td width=\"48\" style=\"padding: 0cm 5.4pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 19px; border-bottom: 1pt outset black; border-left: rgb(212, 208, 200); background-color: transparent; border-top: 1pt outset black; border-right: 1pt o